Manterror/Shockwave/Bumblebee/Double Punch:



Manterror grunted as he was kicked, swinging a clawed hand at Ramulus' left 
knee, his other clawed hand swinging downward at the middle of Ramulus' right 
foot.

---

Shockwave felt the bolt go by him.  Letting himself land to the ground, he 
transformed to robot mode.  Raising an arm, he fired a laser blast from the 
laser weapon embedded in his right hand, simultaneusly firing two blasts from 
his laser rifle in his left hand, all shots heading for Striker.

---

Double Punch slammed into a tree.  His cloak went off.  Raising an arm, he 
saw orange.  "OH SLAG!  MY CLOAK!" he screamed, firing a stinger missile from 
one pincher at Striker, one missile at Triceradon from the other.

---

"Bumblebee, terrorize!" The Predacon yelled, going into robot mode, hovering 
in the air, holding two stinger missile launchers.  Raising one launcher, he 
fired two stinger missiles at Stegotron, two at Ultracon, and two optic 
blasts at the back of Ramulus' left knee.
